10328.description: Cargo stolen from Warehouse Keeper Sonin of Florin Village. Return it to Sonin.

10329.name: Hate Crystal

10334.name: Badge - Temple Executor
10334.description: Give it to High Priest Sylvain along with the Temple of Einhasad's "Temple Executor" proof of identity and the "Badge - Temple Missionary."

10335.name: Giants' Experimental Tool Fragment
10335.description: Relic of the Giants found on the monsters and apostates in the Cruma Marshlands. Bring it to Spellbook Seller Rouke.

10336.name: Giants' Experimental Tool
10336.description: Experimental tool created by the Giants. Use it to lure the apostates in the Cruma Marshlands.

10337.name: Giants' Technology Report
10337.description: Proof of the traitor's defeat in the Cruma Marshlands. Bring it to Spellbook Seller Rouke.

10338.name: Rouke's Report
10338.description: Rouke's Report. Deliver it to Priest Glyvka.

10339.name: Badge - Temple Missionary
10339.description: Give it to High Priest Sylvain along with the Temple of Einhasad's "Temple Missionary" proof of identity and the "Badge - Temple Executor."

10340.name: Report Fragment
10340.description: A piece of the Investigation Report carried by the missing Temple investigator. Bring it to High Priest Sylvain.

10342.name: Relics of the Dark Elf Trainee
10342.description: Relics of a Dark Elf trainee who was killed during live training. Give it to Dark Elf Angus.

10343.name: Angus' Recommendation
10343.description: Token for helping Angus. Show it to Priestess Pupina.

10344.name: Pupina's Recommendation
10344.description: Proof of versatility and the right to contact the preachers. Show it to Preacher Sla.

10345.name: Records Chest Key Fragment
10345.description: Key fragment that is held by the Tasaba Lizardmen. If you bring it to Warehouse Keeper Mia, she can turn it into a Records Chest Key.

10346.name: Records Chest
10346.description: Records chest held by the Tasaba Lizardmen. Bring it to Warehouse Keeper Mia to inspect the contents.

10347.name: Dark Crystal
10347.description: Ingredient needed to create the Dark Oxide. Bring it to Magister Xenovia.

10348.name: Dark Oxide
10348.description: Substance on which Magister Xenovia is experimenting.

10349.name: Cryptogram of the Goddess Sword
10349.description: Secret document about the Sword of Sthelotte that the Goddess of Lake Eva gave to Rionelle, bring it to Kluck.

10350.name: Predecessor's Report
10350.description: Investigate report of the intelligence agency that records the death of Shadow Fox. Bring it to Warehouse Chief Natools.

10351.name: Cryptogram of the Angel Search
10351.description: Clue regarding the angel's location that was discovered by Shadow Fox's intelligence agency. Encoded as a Cryptogram. Decipher it through High Priest Raymond in the Town of Gludio.

10352.name: Prophecy Fragment
10352.description: Prophecy - Path of the God. When all the prophecy fragments are collected, they reveal the Fallen Angel's location.

10353.name: Fallen Angel Blood
10353.description: Proof of the eradication of the angel that was labeled a Fallen Angel by the Temple. Deliver it to High Priest Raymond in the Town of Gludio.

10354.name: Sealed Prophecy - Path of the God
10354.description: Sealed prophecy that foretells the location of the angel. Bring it to Grand Master Tobias in Gludio Castle.

10355.name: Prophecy - Path of the God
10355.description: Prophecy that foretells the location of the angel. Ask Elder Casian of the Wastelands to decipher it.

10356.name: Empty Sound Crystal
10356.description: A sound crystal for saving the angel's message. There is nothing recorded on it yet.

10357.name: Angel Medicine
10357.description: Medicine that Casian made for the injured angel. Administer it to the Fallen Angel.

10358.name: Angel's Message
10358.description: A sound crystal for saving the angel's message. Bring it to Grand Master Tobias in Gludio Castle.

10359.name: Metallograph
